                    <span>I've read a lot of books about Warren Buffett and this is by far my favorite.  If you have to read only one, read this one.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Excellent reading</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
